(26, 124, '语言切换模块', 'language-switcher', '', '<p>语言切换模块将显示一个语言标签来允许用户切换网站的语言。</p>\r\n<p>该模块显示可以供来访者切换的所有语言的列表。</p>\r\n<p>当切换语言的时候，它会重定向到网站主页或者设定好的菜单项，或者所设定的页面。此后，网站导航将按该语言的设置而改变。</p>\r\n<p><strong>要使语言切换模块正常工作，必须开启相关的语言筛选插件。</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong></strong> <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Extensions_Module_Manager_Language_Switcher" title="语言切换模块">帮助（英文）</a></p>\r\n<p>如想查阅一个使用语言切换模块的范例，请登录网站后台，开启语言筛选插件和语言切换模块，并访问示范网站水果店或澳洲公园，然后根据<a href="http://docs.joomla.org/Language_Switcher_Tutorial_for_Joomla_1.6">Joomla语言切换指南</a>操作。</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 67, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:25:00', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 0, 3, 'Joomla 2.5示范网站, 语言切换模块, 多语言示范, 多语言设置', 'Joomla 2.5语言切换模块的介绍', 1, 3, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(27, 125, '最新文章模块', 'latest-articles-module', '', '<p>该模块显示一个最新发布的文章列表。请注意它也会显示已经过期的最新发布的文章。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Extensions_Module_Manager_Latest_News" title="最新文章">帮助（英文）</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule articles_latest,Latest News}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 64, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '', '2011-12-27 11:25:41', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 9, 0, 1, 'Joomla 2.5示范网站, 最新文章模块', 'Joomla 2.5最新文章模块的介绍', 1, 15, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(28, 126, '登录模块', 'login-module', '', '<p>该模块显示一个需填写用户名和密码的登录表单。它也显示一个解决遗忘密码问题的链接。如在"用户管理"的选项里允许用户注册，它还会显示一个让用户可以自行注册的链接。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Extensions_Module_Manager_Login" title="登录模块">帮助</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule login,login}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 65, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-09-17 22:20:35', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 4, 0, 2, '登录模块, Joomla 2.5', 'Joomla 2.5登录模块的介绍', 1, 5, '', 0, '*', ''),
