(32, 130, '选项或参数设置', 'options', '', '<p>当你在构建或使用你的Joomla网站时，通过功能扩展的<em>选项</em>或者<strong>参数设置</strong>，你将能控制网站各部分的细节：从是否显示作者的名字到谁能看到某个列表的条目数。可以说参数控制着网站的一切。</p><p>点击下组件工具栏上的选项按钮，您就能改变每个组件的默认参数。</p><p>参数也可以设置在个别项目上，如一篇文章，或者一个联系人的信息，或者菜单的某个链接。</p><p>如果你对你的网站的外在表现很满意，让您的网站时保持安装后默认的所有参数设置，当然未尝不可。不过当您对Joomla很熟悉之后，您就会自行对一些参数进行调整。</p><p></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 19, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2012-01-17 16:21:24', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 0, 10, '选项或参数设置, 介绍, Joomla 2.5', 'Joomla 2.5选项或参数设置的介绍', 1, 3, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
