(36, 134, '随机图片模块', 'random-image-module', '', '<p>该模块从您选定的目录里随机显示一个图片。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Extensions_Module_Manager_Random_Image" title="随机图片模块">帮助（英文）</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule random_image,Random Image}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 66, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '', '2012-01-17 16:11:13', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 6, 0, 4, 'Joomla 2.5示范网站, 高级用户指南, 囧啦', 'Joomla 2.5随机图片模块的介绍', 1, 6, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(37, 135, '相关文章模块', 'related-items-module', '', '<p>该模块显示与当前被阅读的一篇文章的相关文章——它们之间的关系通过元数据的关键词来确定，即使用被阅读的这篇文章的所有关键词来搜索其它所有已发布的文章。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Extensions_Module_Manager_Articles_Related" title="Related Items Module">帮助（英文）</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule related_items,Articles Related Items}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 64, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:37:34', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 5, 0, 4, '相关文章模块, Joomla 2.5', 'Joomla 2.5相关文章模块的介绍', 1, 5, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(38, 136, '示范网站', 'sample-sites', '', '<p>Joomla在安装时可以安装示范数据。在您建立网站时，示范数据可以给您提供快速入门式的帮助——除了介绍Joomla自身之外，还能给您展示两个网站。</p>\r\n<p>第一个网站是一个<a href="index.php?Itemid=243" target="_blank">澳洲公园</a>有关的简单的网站。它告诉您您可以仅使用Joomla本身快速，轻松地建立一个个人网站！该示范网站包括个人博客、友情链接及一个非常简单的相册。</p>\r\n<p>第二个网站"<a href="index.php?Itemid=429" target="_blank">水果店</a>"稍微复杂一点，旨在告诉您：如果您正在建设一个小型的业务网站，您可以做成什么样。</p>\r\n<p>无论在建立风格类似的网站，还是与以上两个示范完全不同的网站，您都可能要添加的<a href="http://extensions.joomla.org" target="_blank">功能扩展</a>，设计或购买自己喜欢的模板。许多Joomla用户都是通过直接修改Joomla本身所带的核心<a href="http://docs.joomla.org/How_do_you_modify_a_template%3F" target="_blank">模板</a>来开始构建他们的网站，因为这样做能够使他们节省大量的模板设计时间，并把自己的时间和精力集中到网站所需的特殊图片和其他页面元素的设计上。</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 19, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:39:07', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 2, 0, 11, '示范网站, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', '对Joomla 2.5示范网站的介绍', 1, 5, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(39, 137, '站内搜索组件', 'search-component', '', '<p>站内搜索组件提供了搜索Joomla核心组件所包含的信息的基本功能。它同时也能搜索许多第三方开发的功能扩展里的内容。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Components_Search">帮助（英文）</a></p>\r\n<p>智能搜索组件提供与主流搜索引擎（如谷歌）类似的搜索功能。请注意默认情况下智能搜索功能是关闭的。如果您想开启它需要好几个步骤。首先，通过"插件管理"开启智能搜索插件。然后，用智能搜索模块替换掉普通站内搜索模块。最后，如果您的网站已经有了内容，访问管理后台的"智能搜索组件"，点击"索引"按钮。一旦网站内容的索引工作完成，就可以使用智能搜索功能了。</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 21, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:41:48', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 0, 3, '站内搜索, 智能搜索, 站内搜索组件, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', 'Joomla 2.5站内搜索组件的介绍', 1, 3, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(40, 138, '站内搜索模块', 'search-module', '', '<p>该模块显示一个搜索框。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Extensions_Module_Manager_Search" title="站内搜索模块">帮助（英文）</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule search,Search}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 67, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-09-17 22:35:56', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 4, 0, 4, '站内搜索, 智能搜索, 站内搜索模块, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', 'Joomla 2.5站内搜索模块的介绍', 1, 6, '', 0, '*', ''),
(41, 139, '站内搜索插件', 'search-plugin', '', '<p>搜索组件使用插件来控制搜索您的Joomla网站哪些部分。你可以本着提高性能或其他原因，而选择关闭一些区域（即把它们排出在搜索范围内）。许多第三方Joomla功能扩展都有搜索插件，来让Joomla搜索到特定的内容。</p>\r\n<p>默认开启：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>内容 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Search_-_Content">帮助（英文）</a></li>\r\n<li>联系我们 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Search_-_Contacts">帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>友情链接 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Search_-_Weblinks">帮助（英文）</a></li>\r\n<li>新闻联播 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Search_-_Newsfeeds">帮助（英文）</a></li>\r\n<li>文章分类 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Search_-_Categories">帮助（英文）</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 0, 0, 25, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-09-06 06:13:18', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 3, 0, 1, '站内搜索插件, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', '对Joomla 2.5站内搜索插件的介绍', 1, 0, '', 0, '*', ''),
(42, 140, '网站地图模块', 'site-map', '', '<p>{loadposition sitemapload}</p><p><em>通过多级分类来管理您网站的内容（文章等），即可让搜索引擎通过一个菜单，就能收录您网站里的所有内容。</em></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 14, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 1, 0, 1, '网站地图模块, Joomla 2.5, sitemap', 'Joomla 2.5网站地图模块的介绍', 1, 0, '', 0, '*', ''),
