(44, 142, '站内统计模块', 'statistics', '', '<p>该模块显示您网站所在服务器的信息、网站的用户数、网站的文章数以及友情链接数等统计信息。</p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule mod_stats,Statistics}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 67, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:43:25', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 6, 0, 5, 'Joomla 2.5示范网站, 站内统计模块, 囧啦示范', 'Joomla 2.5站内统计模块的介绍', 1, 5, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(45, 143, '联合供稿模块', 'syndicate-module', '', '<p>联合供稿模块显示一个链接，通过该链接可允许用户从您的网站获取新闻源。该模块只显示在可取得新闻源的页面上，这也就是说它不会显示在单篇文章或单个联系人或单个友情链接的页面里（比如本页）。<a href="http://docs.joomla.org/Help15:Screen.modulessite.edit.15#Syndicate" title="联合供稿模块">帮助（英文）</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadposition syndicate,Syndicate}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 67, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '', '2011-12-27 11:44:16', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 0, 6, 'Joomla 2.5示范网站, 联合供稿模块, 囧啦示范', 'Joomla 2.5联合供稿模块的介绍', 1, 2, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(46, 144, '系统插件', 'system', '', '<p>在您的站点输出每个页面的时候，系统插件都在起作用。它们控制着您网站里的所有地址，控制着用户登录时能否勾选登录模块里的"记住我"，以及是否启用缓存，等等。Joomla 2.5的新功能是用插件与重定向组件配合，协助您来变化网址。</p>\r\n<p>默认开启：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>记住我 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_Remember_Me">帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>搜索引擎友好链接 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_SEF">帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>调试（Debug） <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_Debug">帮助</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>默认关闭：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>缓存 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_Cache">帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>登录 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_Log">帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>重定向 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#System_-_Redirect">帮助</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 0, 0, 25, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:45:54', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 5, 0, 2, 'Joomla 2.5示范网站, 系统插件, 囧啦示范', 'Joomla 2.5系统插件的介绍', 1, 1, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(47, 145, 'Joomla!社区', 'the-joomla-community', '', '<p>Joomla的字面意思是"团结在一起"，实际上它也的确是一个大家一起工作和一起享受于其中的Joomla社区！每年都有成千上万的人加入Joomla社区，我们希望您将是其中之一。</p>\r\n<p>我们欢迎世界各地拥有各种技能的加入社区！Joomla社区的核心是网站<a href="http://joomla.org">Joomla.org</a>（它的<a href="http://forum.joomla.org" target="_blank">论坛</a>是一个很好的起点）。参加<a href="http://community.joomla.org/events.html" target="_blank">Joomla交流活动</a>，或者加入一个<a href="http://community.joomla.org/user-groups.html" target="_blank">Joomla用户组</a>……无论您是程序员、网站管理员、设计师、网站使用者或Joomla粉丝，这里都有办法让您参与和贡献您的力量。</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 19, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:47:56', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 0, 3, 'Joomla!社区', '对Joomla!社区的介绍', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(48, 146, 'Joomla!项目', 'the-joomla-project', '', '<p>在Joomla项目包括了所有设计和支持Joomla网络平台和内容管理系统的人们！</p>\r\n<p>我们的使命是提供一个灵活的数字化出版和协作的平台。</p>\r\n<p>我们的核心价值观：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>自由</li>\r\n<li>平等</li>\r\n<li>信任</li>\r\n<li>社区</li>\r\n<li>协作</li>\r\n<li>实用性</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>我们的愿景：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>全球各地的人通过他们的社区出版和协作</li>\r\n<li>软件是免费、安全和高品质的</li>\r\n<li>一个快乐而有益的社区</li>\r\n<li>世界各地的人们可使用他们喜欢的语言</li>\r\n<li>一个行为自主的项目</li>\r\n<li>一个能够承担社会负责的项目</li>\r\n<li>一个能始终值得其用户信赖的项目</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Joomla在世界各地已有千百万用户和千万对Joomla项目有所贡献的人们。他们工作在三个主要群体：产品开发组（负责软件开发和文档的编纂）；社区交流组（为创造一个有教养的社会而工作）；Open Source Matters（这是一个非营利组织，负责管理Joomla的法律、金融和组织等方面的问题）。</p>\r\n<p>Joomla！是一个自由和开放源码项目，它遵循GNU通用公共许可证协议第二版或更高版本。</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 19, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '', '2011-12-27 11:47:48', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 2, 0, 1, 'Joomla!项目', '对Joomla!项目的介绍', 1, 1, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(49, 147, '字体样式', 'typography', '', '<h1>H1 ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ abcdefghijklmonpqrstuvwzyz</h1><h2>H2 ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ abcdefghijklmonpqrstuvwzyz</h2><h3>H3 ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ abcdefghijklmonpqrstuvwzyz</h3><h4>H4 ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ abcdefghijklmonpqrstuvwzyz</h4><h5>H5 ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ abcdefghijklmonpqrstuvwzyz</h5><h6>H6 ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ abcdefghijklmonpqrstuvwzyz</h6><p>P The quick brown fox ran over the lazy dog. THE QUICK BROWN FOX RAN OVER THE LAZY DOG.</p><ul><li>Item</li><li>Item</li><li>Item<br /> <ul><li>Item</li><li>Item</li><li>Item<br /> <ul><li>Item</li><li>Item</li><li>Item</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><ol><li>tem</li><li>Item</li><li>Item<br /> <ol><li>Item</li><li>Item</li><li>Item<br /><ol><li>Item</li><li>Item</li><li>Item</li></ol></li></ol> </li></ol>', '', 1, 0, 0, 23, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 1, 0, 1, 'Joomla!字体样式', '对Joomla!字体样式的介绍', 1, 0, '', 0, '*', ''),
(50, 148, '进阶用户', 'upgraders', '', '<p>如您是经验丰富的Joomla1.5用户，1.6对您来说就会驾轻就熟。虽然囧啦1.6的模板机制有了新变化，并且对用户界面也做了改进，但囧啦的大多数的功能大同小异。Joomla 2.5 最大的变化在于提高了访问控制（ACL）和文章分类的无限化。</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>另外，新的用户管理处可以让您对不同的用户在您的网站能访问的内容作出严格的控制。您可以像Joomla 1.5那样管理用户的访问权限，也可以按更复杂的方式去管理。您可以通过<a href="http://docs.joomla.org" target="_blank">官方的Joomla文档库</a>学习<a href="http://docs.joomla.org/ACL_Tutorial_for_Joomla_1.6" target="_blank">如何设置用户的访问权限</a>。</p>\r\n<p>在Joomla 1.5和1.0中，文章是通过"文章单元"和"文章分类"，来分门别类管理的。1.6剔除了"文章单元"，而采用了文章可以无限分类的机制。本示范网站即提供了很多分类管理文章的示例。</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>囧啦所有的用户界面都已以提高可访问性和灵活性为核心而重新设计。如果您想保留1.5布局，您可以在模板MilkyWay的文件夹html中找到，并只需将它复制到您的模板的相同文件夹中即可使用。</p>\r\n<p>囧啦的安装器可以让您比以往更容易地升级您的网站或其功能扩展。</p>\r\n<p>如您想了解有关如何将一个Joomla1.5网站升级到Joomla 2.5安装，<a href="http://docs.joomla.org/Migrating_from_1.5_to_1.6" target="_blank">请参阅本文</a>。</p>\r\n<p></p>', 1, 0, 0, 19, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '', '2012-01-17 04:28:10', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 5, 0, 6, '囧啦, Joomla 2.5简体中文版，中级用户', '对囧啦中级用户介绍Joomla 2.5', 1, 3, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 1, '*', ''),
(51, 149, '用户插件', 'user-plugins', '', '<p>默认开启：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Joomla <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#User_-_Joomla.21">帮助</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>默认关闭：</p>\r\n<p>Joomla 2.5 有两个相关的用户插件，不过默认情况下它们都是关闭状态。</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>"联系人"创建器 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#User_-_Contact_Creator">帮助</a><br />为每一个新创建的用户创建一个新的联系人链接。</li>\r\n<li>个人资料 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#User_-_Profile">帮助</a><br />这个示范性的插件允许您在用户注册表增加额外的字段，并显示于个人资料页面里。这只是通过示范告诉您，您也许需要创建的一个用户资料的扩展的类型。</li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 0, 0, 25, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:51:25', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 0, 4, '用户插件, Joomla 2.5', 'Joomla 2.5用户插件的介绍', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(52, 150, '用户管理组件', 'users-component', '', '<p>\r\n<p>用户管理组件让您网站的访问者可以注册、登录或注销、修改密码等个人信息、找回丢失的密码。在后台它则允许您创建、封杀用户，或创建用户组、设定其访问权限，等等。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Users_User_Manager">帮助（英文）</a></p>\r\n<p>请注意，如果您未登录站点，您可能就看不到网站的某些内容。</p>\r\n</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 21, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-01-10 04:52:55', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":""}', 2, 0, 5, '用户管理组件, Joomla 2.5', 'Joomla 2.5用户管理组件的介绍', 1, 1, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(53, 151, '使用Joomla!', 'using-joomla', '', '<p>有了Joomla，从简单的个人网站，到复杂的电子商务网站，到数百万访客的社交网站，您可以打造出各种各样的网站。</p><p>这部分示范内容提供的是对Joomla的基本概念的简要介绍。这些参考材料可以帮助您了解Joomla的工作原理。</p><p><strong>当您不再需要这些示范内容时，您只需通过后台取消发布这些示范内容所在的分类即可——或者您也可以直接删除与此相关的所有文章、菜单和分类。</strong></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 19, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:52:45', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 2, 0, 7, 'Joomla简介', 'Joomla简介', 1, 9, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(54, 152, '友情链接组件', 'weblinks', '', '<p>友情链接组件（com_weblinks以一种结构化的方式来管理外部链接，让它们视觉上一目了然、能够吸引眼球并给用户提供足够的信息。以一种结构化的方式来管理外部链接，让它们视觉上一目了然、能够吸引眼球并给用户提供足够的信息。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Components_Weblinks_Links">帮助（英文）</a></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 21, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-01-10 04:20:10', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":""}', 2, 0, 6, '友情链接组件, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', 'Joomla 2.5友情链接组件的介绍', 1, 3, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
