(60, 158, '新闻联播组件', 'news-feeds', '', '<p>新闻联播组件（com_newsfeeds）提供了一种在您的网站里组织和发布源于其它网站的新闻的方式。例如，joomla.org有许多新闻联播源（又叫新闻供稿）是您可以在您的网站里直接调用的。您可使用菜单发布一个联播新闻，或一个分类里的一组联播新闻，或所有分类里的所有联播新闻。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Components_Newsfeeds_Feeds">帮助（英文）</a></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 21, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:27:31', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 3, 0, 4, '新闻联播组件, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', 'Joomla 2.5新闻联播组件的介绍', 1, 2, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(61, 159, '面包屑（导航）模块', 'breadcrumbs-module', '', '<p>面包屑（导航）模块为访问本网站的人提供一个路径导航<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Extensions_Module_Manager_Breadcrumbs" title="面包屑模块">帮助（英文）</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule breadcrumbs,breadcrumbs}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 75, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-09-17 22:10:19', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":""}', 5, 0, 2, '面包屑（导航）模块, 导航模块, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', 'Joomla 2.5面包屑（导航）模块的介绍', 1, 9, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(62, 160, '内容插件', 'content-plugins', '', '<p>内容插件只有在加载特定类型的页面时才运行。它们的作用可以是保护Email地址免受垃圾邮件之苦，也可以是创建分页符，等等。</p>\r\n<p>默认开启：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Email地址保护 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Email_Cloaking">帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>加载模块 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Load_Modules">帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>分页 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Pagebreak">帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>页面导航 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Page_Navigation"> 帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>文章评级 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Vote">帮助</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>默认关闭：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>代码高亮显示（Geshi） <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Code_Highlighter_.28GeSHi.29">帮助</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 0, 0, 25, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-09-06 06:11:50', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 2, 0, 7, '内容插件, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', '对Joomla 2.5内容插件的介绍', 1, 1, '', 0, '*', ''),
