(67, 168, 'Joomla 2.5的新变化', 'whats-new-in-15', '', '<p>Joomla 2.5 更强大！更适用！更灵活多变！囧啦！</p><p>Joomla 2.5 的简体中文语言，是我们简体中文翻译小组提供的（交流网站：<a href="http://www.joomla.cn" target=_blank>囧啦!中国</a>）！囧啦！</p><p>Joomla 2.5面目一新，并且拥有很多的实用功能。它将成为大家在广域网、局域网或手机网站等领域构建小型、中型和大型企业级网站最有力的助手！</p><p>"简捷而强大"是Joomla一贯的宗旨，也是它成为内容管理系统领头羊的重要法宝！</p><p>Joomla 2.5的功能特色：</p><p>1、出色的的用户权限控制：从访问内容到编辑内容，用户的权限控制非常灵活和严谨；<br>2、无限极分类：这是Joomla 1.5望尘莫及的；<br>3、强大的功能扩展安装系统：一个包，多个功能扩展的安装，没问题！<br>4、加强对多语言的支持；</p><p>5、模块发布时间和位置的控制更精准：<br>6、新的模板机制和语义标记(semantic markup)：让浏览更便利，让搜索引擎的收录也更便利；</p><p>7、模板样式的更有创造力的控制；<br>8、数百个附件功能特性、流线形的工作流和生产力；</p><p>Joomla 2.5 还将让功能扩展的开发、升级变得更容易！</p><p>先进并且丰富的API接口，为使用者在新市场里的整合、竞争和拓展提供了新的机遇！</p><p>模板机制的加强让设计者有了更强大也更灵活的为任何网站或任何人，设计出更完美的效果。模板设计师可以通过模板覆盖控制网站所有内容的输出效果，从而为网站的功能控制、易用性甚至在手机平台的应用带来新的机会。个性化的后台模板机制能使主人为不同的管理员而量身定制不同的后台管理。</p>', '', 2, 0, 0, 9, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla! 1.5', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 1, 0, 0, 'Joomla 2.5的功能介绍, Joomla 2.5的新变化, 囧啦', 'Joomla 2.5的新变化', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(68, 170, '验证码插件', 'captcha', '', '<p>验证码插件是一个新的核心插件。现在您可以更容易地为您网站的注册、登录和联系添加验证码。Joomla网站安装时所带的验证码插件利用的是ReCaptcha®服务，您可以通过安装其它插件而连接到不同的验证码系统。</p>\r\n<p>默认开启：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>ReCaptcha <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit">帮助（英文）</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>备注：ReCaptcha是谷歌公司的注册商标，并且是一个与Joomla项目无关的产品。要使用该插件，您需要接受Recaptcha.net的服务器协议。在"插件管理"里，当您编辑验证码插件时您能够看到全面的介绍。</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 25, '2012-01-17 03:20:45', 42, 'Joomla!', '2012-01-17 03:35:46', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-01-17 03:20:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 2, 0, 1, '验证码插件, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', 'Joomla 2.5验证码插件的介绍', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(69, 171, '快捷图标插件', 'quick-icons', '', '<p>快捷图标插件是一个快捷图标群，用以给您提供Joomla更新或者您安装的第三方扩展更新的通知。这些通知显示于管理后台的控制面板里。</p>\r\n<p>默认开启：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>快捷图标 - Joomla!扩展更新通知 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit">帮助（英文）</a>。</li>\r\n<li>快捷图标 - Joomla!更新通知 <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit">帮助</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 0, 0, 25, '2012-01-17 03:27:39', 42, 'Joomla!', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-01-17 03:27:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 1, 0, 0, '快捷图标插件, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', 'Joomla 2.5快捷图标插件的介绍', 1, 0, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(70, 170, '智能搜索模块', 'smart-search', '', '<p>智能搜索模块使用智能搜索组件为用户提供站内搜索功能。您只要在您已经索引您网站的内容并且已经开启智能搜索插件（否则要一直手工更新网站的索引）时才能使用它。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help25:Extensions_Module_Manager_Smart_Search">帮助</a>。</p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule finder,Smart Search}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 67, '2012-01-17 03:42:36', 42, '', '2012-01-17 16:15:48', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-01-17 03:42:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 10, 0, 0, '智能搜索模块, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', 'Joomla 2.5智能搜索模块的介绍', 1, 13, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', '');

