(14, 39, 1, 9, 56, 1, 'sample-data-articles', 'com_content', '示范文章', 'sample-data-articles', '', '<p>这是Joomla 2.5.x里的示范文章。由Joomla简体中文翻译组翻译。建议请反馈至：<a href="http://www.joomla.cn" target="_blank">joomla.cn</a>，或新浪微群：<a href="http://q.weibo.com/916533" target="_blank">Joomla交流</a>。谢谢！</p>', 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, '{"target":"","image":""}', 'Joomla 2.5.x里的示范文章的分类', 'Joomla 2.5.x,示范文章的分类,囧啦', '{"page_title":"","author":"Joomla","robots":""}', 42, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 0, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 0, '*'),
