(65, 94, 22, 17, 18, 5, 'sample-data-articles/joomla/extensions/modules/user-modules', 'com_content', '用户模块', 'user-modules', '', '<p>用户模块协调于"用户系统"插件，使用户能够登录网站，并能显示谁登录了网站以及最近注册的用户名单。</p>', 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, '{"category_layout":"","image":""}', '', '', '{"author":"","robots":""}', 42, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '2011-12-27 12:00:50', 0, '*'),
(66, 95, 22, 19, 20, 5, 'sample-data-articles/joomla/extensions/modules/display-modules', 'com_content', '展示模块', 'display-modules', '', '<p>该类模块可以显示内容和用户之外的信息，包括友情链接、新闻联播和多媒体。</p>', 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, '{"target":"","image":""}', '', '', '{"page_title":"","author":"","robots":""}', 42, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 0, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 0, '*'),
(67, 96, 22, 21, 22, 5, 'sample-data-articles/joomla/extensions/modules/utility-modules', 'com_content', '工具模块', 'utility-modules', '', '<p>工具模块提供诸如搜索、新闻供稿、站内统计等有用的功能。</p>', 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, '{"category_layout":"","image":""}', '', '', '{"author":"","robots":""}', 42, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '2011-12-27 12:01:34', 0, '*'),
(68, 97, 23, 31, 32, 5, 'sample-data-articles/joomla/extensions/templates/atomic', 'com_content', 'Atomic', 'atomic', '', '<p><img src="templates/atomic/template_thumbnail.png" border="0" alt="模板Atomic" style="border: 0; float: right;" /></p>\r\n<p>Atomic是最小巧的一个模板，如果您想了解Joomla 2.5的模板，或者您想设计一个模板，您都应该以它为起点。</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="index.php?Itemid=285">首页</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="index.php?Itemid=316">字体样式</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>', 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, '{"category_layout":"","image":""}', '', '', '{"author":"","robots":""}', 42, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '2011-12-27 12:08:16', 0, '*'),
(69, 98, 23, 27, 28, 5, 'sample-data-articles/joomla/extensions/templates/beez-20', 'com_content', 'Beez 20', 'beez-20', '', '<p><img src="templates/beez_20/template_thumbnail.png" border="0" alt="模板Beez_20的缩略图" align="right" style="float: right;" /></p>\r\n<p>Beez 2.0是一个多功能、易于定制、适用广泛的模板。它展示了Joomla模板的易用性和标准性，及css样式和javasript脚本应用技术。它是Joomla 2.5的默认模板。</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="index.php?Itemid=424">首页</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="index.php?Itemid=423">字体样式</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, '{"category_layout":"","image":""}', '', '', '{"author":"","robots":""}', 42, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 0, '*'),
(70, 99, 23, 29, 30, 5, 'sample-data-articles/joomla/extensions/templates/beez-5', 'com_content', 'Beez 5', 'beez-5', '', '<p><img src="templates/beez5/template_thumbnail.png" border="0" alt="模板Beez5的缩略图" align="right" style="float: right;" /></p>\r\n<p>Beez 5是html5在Joomla模板里应用的一个典范。它通过应用html5技术提升了网站的表现力。示范网站"水果店"使用的即是该模板。</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href="index.php?Itemid=458">首页</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="index.php?Itemid=457">字体样式</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, '{"category_layout":"","image":""}', '', '', '{"author":"","robots":""}', 42, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '2011-12-27 12:06:57', 0, '*'),
