(12, 110, '自定义HTML模块', 'custom-html-module', '', '<p>该模块允许您使用可见可得编辑器创建您自己需要的HTML模块。<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Extensions_Module_Manager_Custom_HTML" title="自定义HTML模块">帮助（英文）</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule custom,Custom HTML}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 66, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '', '2011-12-27 11:12:46', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 13, 0, 1, 'Joomla 2.5 示范网站, 自定义HTML模块, 囧啦示范', 'Joomla 2.5 自定义HTML模块的介绍', 1, 13, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(13, 111, '交通指南', 'directions', '', '<p></p>\r\n<p>如何找到我们的店？</p>\r\n<p>开车</p>\r\n<p>驱车沿达坂路，到达与吐鲁番大道交叉的路口，即可寻找到我们的标志。</p>\r\n<p>步行</p>\r\n<p>从镇中心，沿吐鲁番大道一直向北走，直到看到我们的标志（达坂路与吐鲁番大道交叉处）。</p>\r\n<p>乘坐公交</p>\r\n<p>乘73路大巴到最后一站。我们正处在该站点东北角落。</p>\r\n<p></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 29, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, '水果店网站管理员', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 1, 0, 2, 'Joomla 2.5 示范网站, 示范文章, 囧啦示范', 'Joomla 2.5 示范网站里的一篇示范文章', 1, 0, '', 0, '*', ''),
(14, 112, '编辑器', 'editors', '', '<p>在编写内容时，我们就需要用到像Microsoft Word那样的编辑器。Joomla默认使用最广泛的编辑器是TinyMCE。但当我们管理模板时默认使用的则是CodeMirror。如不使用编辑器则在编辑内容时，您面临的就是一个供您进行html页面编辑的文本录入框。</p>\r\n<p>默认开启：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>CodeMirror <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Editor_-_CodeMirror">帮助（英文）</a></li>\r\n<li>TinyMCE<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Editor_-_TinyMCE"> Help</a></li>\r\n<li>不使用编辑器<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Editor_-_None">帮助（英文）</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>默认关闭：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>None</li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 0, 0, 25, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-09-06 05:45:40', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 2, 0, 5, '编辑器, 插件, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', '对Joomla 2.5编辑器插件的介绍', 1, 0, '', 0, '*', ''),
(15, 113, '编辑器插件', 'editors-xtd', '', '<p>这些插件通常在编辑器下方的按钮后面。它们仅在编辑器运行时才开始运行。</p>\r\n<p>默认开启：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>编辑器按钮：插入图片<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Button_-_Image"> Help</a></li>\r\n<li>编辑器按钮：插入"阅读全文..."<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Button_-_Readmore">帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>编辑器按钮：插入分页符<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Button_-_Pagebreak">帮助</a></li>\r\n<li>编辑器按钮：文章标题链接<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Button_-_Article">帮助</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>默认关闭：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>无</li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 0, 0, 25, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-12-27 11:14:12', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":"","urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":"","urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":"","urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 0, 6, '编辑器插件, Joomla 2.5, 囧啦', '对Joomla 2.5 编辑器插件的介绍', 1, 1, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
